# Prevent provisioned core/.claude/ patterns from polluting hub-only .claude/
# Hub-only .claude/ files are tracked explicitly; everything else is ignored.
# If you need to add a new hub-only pattern, use `git add -f .claude/path`.
.claude/config/
.claude/sync-manifest.json
CLAUDE.local.md

# Prompt log — contains raw user prompts captured by prompt-logger.sh hook,
# may include secrets/PII. The seed at core/.claude/tasks/prompts.md stays
# tracked so provisioning can copy it into downstream projects.
/.claude/tasks/prompts.md
